Package: finSCB
Type: Package
Title: An R interface to the web API of Statistics Finland
Version: 0.3.4
Date: 2014-07-21
Author: Love Hansson, Leo Lahti, Mans Magnusson
Maintainer: Mans Magnusson <louhos@googlegroups.com>
Description: Interface for the REST API of Statistics Finland. The
    package offers methods to fetch information about the data hierarchy stored
    behind the API; extract metadata; fetch actual data; and clean up the
    results. Based on a similar package for Sweden, the sweSCB.
Imports:
    data.table,
    stringr,
    RJSONIO,
    httr
License: AGPL-3
Suggests:
    testthat,
    ggplot2
